1. *Gadno* me je što sam ti to rekao. (It's awful that I said that to you.)
2. Čuo sam da je bilo *gadno*. (I heard it was awful.)
3. Njegov pogled je bio *gadan*. (His look was awful.)
4. Ušlo je u sobu i okrenulo se u *gadnu* grimasu. (It entered the room and turned into an awful grimace.)
5. Njega je njegovo ponašanje dovelo u veoma *gadnu* situaciju. (His behavior brought him into a very awful situation.)